----------------------------------------------------
!! This directory is currently under construction !!
----------------------------------------------------

Maintainer: jloeser@suse.de
TFTPboot directory: /srv/tftpboot/

* Network boot process:

    x86_64-efi          : grub2/bootx86.efi > grub2/grub.efi
    x86_64-legacy (pxe) : grub2/grub.pxe
    ppc64               : grub2/grub.ppc64.biendian
    ppc64le             : grub2/grub.ppc64le

* Source order (n: required; (n): optional):

     1   grub2/grub.cfg                                 [ do not touch! ] generic root configuration
     2   grub2/00-config/<mac-address>                  [ do not touch! ] autogenerated; machine specific variables
    (3)  grub2/<arch>/02-orthos-install/<mac_address>   [ do not touch! ] autogenerated, optional; sets grub2 default and timeout if triggered
    (4)  grub2/<arch>/01-grub.cfg                       [ do not touch! ] optional; arch specific variables
    (5)  grub2/<arch>/90-custom/<mac_address>                             optional; add your machine specific configuration HERE
     6   grub2/<arch>/05-*.cfg                          [ do not touch! ] arch specific template files for SLE, openSUSE, ...

* Reset default after machine setup was triggered:

    grub2/scripts/setup-reset.py

    - use 'rcsetup-reset start|stop'
    - logfile : /var/log/grub2/reset

* Create machine specific stub:

    grub2/scripts/setup.py

    - no manual interaction needed; triggered by Orthos
    - e.g.:
        grub2/scripts/setup.py -a x86_64 -m 00:11:22:33:44:55 -f foobar.suse.de --serial-console true --serial-line 1
